snippet.title: Antichamber Ep. 1
snippet.description:
Welcome to my playthrough (with commentary) of Antichamber, a nearly impossible to describe psychological puzzle game. Join me as I attempt to understand the bizarre universe of Antichamber.

Learn more about this game from the main site:
http://www.antichamber-game.com/

Or from this interesting interview with the creator, Alexander Bruce:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WvgZP-s0cdk
